column5:
Yup. My daughter begs me to tell her stories from when I was a kid. Two problems: 1. After my mom died and dad remarried narcissist stepmom, most stories are painful/abusive. 2. I have huge memory gaps and can't recall a lot of my childhood after 10yrs old. 

&#x200B;

I've told her the few stories I actually remember that aren't shitty. Then I just make up stories about princesses and superheroes and villains.
